WEBVTT

02:25.235 --> 02:26.987
(Beverly) Sure I have.

02:27.076 --> 02:31.546
- Well, I've discovered why sex is.
- You have? Fantastic!

02:31.636 --> 02:34.434
It's because humans
don't live underwater.

02:35.476 --> 02:37.034
I don't get it.

02:37.115 --> 02:42.634
Fish don't need sex, because they just lay
the eggs and fertilise them in the water.

02:42.715 --> 02:45.947
Humans can't do that
because they don't live in water.

02:46.036 --> 02:49.995
They have to... internalise the water.
Therefore we have sex.

02:50.076 --> 02:54.035
So you mean humans wouldn't have sex
if they lived in the water?

02:54.117 --> 02:59.474
They'd have a kind of sex. The kind where
you wouldn't have to touch each other.

02:59.556 --> 03:01.114
I like that idea.

03:01.196 --> 03:04.348
Have you heard of scuba diving?
It's just new.

03:04.437 --> 03:07.668
Self-contained underwater
breathing apparatus.

03:07.757 --> 03:09.315
Exactly.

03:11.957 --> 03:16.235
- Are you thinking what I'm thinking?
- Yeah. You ask her.

03:22.037 --> 03:26.474
Raffaella, will you have sex with us
in our bathtub? It's an experiment.

03:26.557 --> 03:30.267
Are you kidding?
Fuck off, you freaks!

03:30.358 --> 03:32.666
I'm telling my father you talk dirty.

03:32.757 --> 03:36.909
Besides, I know for a fact
you don't even know what "fuck" is!

03:44.638 --> 03:46.629
They're so different from us,...

03:46.719 --> 03:49.709
..and all because
we don't live underwater.

03:54.438 --> 03:56.871
The morculum is working superbly.

03:56.959 --> 04:00.393
- Shall I insert the manticulator?
- Please.

04:04.719 --> 04:06.675
What's the diagnosis?

04:07.479 --> 04:09.435
Intra-ovular surgery.

04:45.120 --> 04:47.680
Where did you get that instrument?

04:48.319 --> 04:50.880
- We had it made for us.
- Really?

05:07.000 --> 05:10.993
Might be fine for a cadaver.
It won't work with a living patient.

05:11.080 --> 05:12.833
(drops instrument)

05:17.841 --> 05:19.796
To our fabulous twins,...

05:19.881 --> 05:22.714
..who have, as mere undergraduates,...

05:22.801 --> 05:25.315
..already brought us glory.

05:25.400 --> 05:26.675
(all) Hear, hear!

05:27.762 --> 05:29.717
And here it is,...

05:31.082 --> 05:32.640
..in solid gold...

05:32.722 --> 05:35.872
Er, well, solid gold plate, that is!

05:35.962 --> 05:37.519
(laughter)

05:37.602 --> 05:41.675
The Mantle retractor, which is now
the standard of the industry.

05:41.761 --> 05:44.719
Here's to a brilliant future!

05:46.042 --> 05:47.997
(cheering)

05:58.722 --> 06:00.280
Here it is.

06:02.642 --> 06:04.201
That's wonderful!

06:04.282 --> 06:05.431
Yeah.

06:16.763 --> 06:18.833
