about the inside of my body before.

08:47.689 --> 08:50.838
Surely you've heard of inner beauty?

08:55.247 --> 08:59.527
I've often thought there should be
beauty contests for the insides of bodies.

08:59.608 --> 09:01.280
You know, best spleen...

09:01.368 --> 09:06.648
