19:41.668 --> 19:43.626
(Claire sobs)

19:45.669 --> 19:47.226
Shh, shh.

19:47.309 --> 19:49.870
What's the matter, what's the matter?

19:57.709 --> 19:59.666
I'll never get pregnant.

20:03.030 --> 20:04.987
