It wouldn't be part of my body.

20:35.031 --> 20:36.986
Yes... that's true.

20:39.512 --> 20:42.071
Don't tell. Please don't tell...

20:43.871 --> 20:46.830
..anybody about me. Please don't tell.

20:49.271 --> 20:53.025
