little organs.

23:45.757 --> 23:49.148
But with the kind of help
we can offer the process,...

23:49.238 --> 23:53.789
..it is possible to...
modify several other organs:

23:53.878 --> 23:55.833
..the odd vein,...

23:55.918 --> 23:57.476
..or, as today,...

23:57.558 --> 24:00.834
