25:21.160 --> 25:23.594
- Is that true?
- Yep.

25:23.679 --> 25:25.433
Do you take drugs?

25:27.001 --> 25:28.353
No.

25:28.441 --> 25:30.033
Well, for pain.

25:31.241 --> 25:33.959
Pain creates character distortion.

25:35.761 --> 25:37.955
